Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz25.43\move(864,42,878,120,26,902)}大太法師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz30.69\move(394,46,392,100)}太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(34,362)}請\N注\N意\N白\N天\N到\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要畫設計圖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我們在設計什麼東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要拼起來就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們打釘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊這麼順利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這種時候不冷靜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想不到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主意 主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬家裡 廁所門上不是有個把手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怎麼看都像隻鴨子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 小夏想到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越用力想 越是什麼都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼新奇的主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非小夏 真的覺得我什麼都沒想到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我一直在裝沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡思考這種尖端科技了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是折刀的刀柄部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 自信爆表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 如果你叫我『會走路的活字典』我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活字典本來就會走路的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我來劃線做標記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏用鋸子沿線鋸木板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋸完之後要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按我說的順序釘上釘子固定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先用那塊板作為底座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那塊大板立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是蓮醬想出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我都覺得做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 這是用來幹什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我現在就用一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要睡覺啊 還管不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 最後做成這樣了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 書架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是咖哩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要開始上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的咖哩和蓮華…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個組合…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過蓮華應該不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢也想不到本校會發生那種大悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下課啦 下課啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去玩積木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把娃娃帶到學校呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生沒問題呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課的時候是收起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老師看到的話要沒收的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師說過上課的時候不要玩就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 今天日影休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明昨天還是活蹦亂跳的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 今天的午餐是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影那份也可以吃掉了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 好歹稍微關心下日影呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那木實就只有一份咖哩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行 我也很想多吃咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曹操到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得好晚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了點麻煩事所以遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 遲到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~行呀 不~行呀 我~要告訴老~師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐背著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影 學校不準帶那種東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老師看到的話要沒收的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 在動呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們把我家妹妹當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母發燒去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我在學校照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才遲到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話請假不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是咖哩 所以不能請假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 竟然記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼賣零食的 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師說了 年紀最大的賣零食的要負責照顧蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 這種事情木實更適合做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說 決定好的事情也不會改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了喔大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂木實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 小夏和小鞠一起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛君也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我抱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會哄小孩子 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華見到有興趣的東西就會咬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎 她很喜歡你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濕嗒嗒的 我要去洗一下校服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華的奶嘴掉地上了 我也要去洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要創造積木高度的新紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那兩個人把小孩丟下跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這孩子已經會走路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的過來了呀 好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的最高紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高紀錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高紀錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只剩下一塊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 一點小事哭什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之後我把零食分你一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害呢 小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經三年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生小吉先生 小吉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生濕嗒嗒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華她… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非去走廊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊裡沒看見呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進配膳室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叫人操心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主菜桶 你準備對咖哩做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華把咖哩當成人質… 咖哩質了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 Stop Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩咖哩咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待很久的咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩咖哩咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 蓮醬第一次上學就把學校鎮壓下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法忘記那個瞬間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚送的梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞌睡防止裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是蓮華做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要怎麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打掃差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書得放好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 踩到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什麼呀 彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比以前更破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破成這樣不能要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫忙找一下我的彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到的話會很痛 所以要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表情怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和體檢完之後的表情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我踩到你的彈力球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便跑進我的房間玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來在那裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是寶物的話為什麼會丟在我的房間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是丟在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是剛好找到以前喜歡的彈力球 丟著玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不還是在丟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 接下來要做什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要把書收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼時候的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老的照片了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為什麼我臉上有傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得是小吉先生掉到門外 去撿的時候摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 沒預先聯繫就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 外面很熱呢 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢好像做了不少我的布娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上什麼都沒有卻摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自做的那些布娃娃果然還是很糟糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不糟糕呀 做得很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候喜歡的娃娃變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓你教我怎麼樣把它補好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁 裁縫工具在我的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以進螢的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也帶了裁縫工具過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了這麼多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢真的很喜歡娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這方面很像個小學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呀 也不要只做我的娃娃 做點其他人的娃娃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都做一樣的很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不會無聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能補好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經破得很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是覺得用新布重新做一個可能會更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就會變成另一個娃娃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要打補丁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那裡應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢做得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩 沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了 螢下次來我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 吃晚餐了 來拿餐具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 那個彈力球怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回壁櫥的玩具箱裡面了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心不要再丟掉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然後悔也沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然學起大人說話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大人了呀
Comment: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急呼救嗎 這是緊急呼救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 Stop
